{"tid":303672,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"信有鬼既人有冇諗過鬼冇腦點思考","createTime":"2017-06-30T10:52:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T09:53:04.000Z","uid":27821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"550ea6d3485a7fc10715c56c04e028c463df2ede","tid":303672,"uid":27821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:52:57.000Z","msg":"冇腦都可以思考害人搵替身既<br />\n個腦有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfccf31ed268dd4f9ddca670c3fb5d8a020d2f9","tid":303672,"uid":17426,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"子非鬼，焉知鬼無腦"},{"pid":"fe8e62c9a704f19ea1f86c37785f604ca6c2027e","tid":303672,"uid":27821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:14:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>子非鬼，焉知鬼無腦</blockquote><br />\n你死左身上個個咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6d7523d23b28faf6c59582a8b4c9232a459023","tid":303672,"uid":63,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"證明思考唔係經大腦 而係靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706c1933816516ed2335cfc886bf95027f24f26d","tid":303672,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"你諗下你點思考咪知鬼點思考囉"},{"pid":"a50cb7936cc7b803f32de72f3e5f3764e1329513","tid":303672,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇腦都可以思考害人搵替身既<br />\n個腦有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔信有鬼<br />\n<br />\n但如果有鬼，因為鬼冇左生前腦，所以佢唔會好似生前咁思考。<br />\n<br />\n但思考同行為（behavior），係可以分開的。鬼可以有行為（傾向搵某種特徵既人附身，比人打擾會有咩本能反應），但呢d行為唔一定要識思考先有。正如細胞都冇腦，但一樣有行為（migration, division , programmed cell death &hellip;etc）<br />\n<br />\n但呢個係一個好好既例證，證明鬼唔係一般小說所描述咁咁有人性。因為人性源自大腦。"},{"pid":"4c7b5698d379bbd485fd818d37528e862b5dbe08","tid":303672,"uid":27821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你諗下你點思考咪知鬼點思考囉</blockquote><br />\n科學都証實左大腦唔同區域既功能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7650e0e07a67e7ebb56a485168cee6df50c1e136","tid":303672,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:55:08.000Z","msg":"咁現實係冇鬼，有咩可以討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81ec1fa70f662e4cd5d9ef6d5a10fa7da163fdc","tid":303672,"uid":27821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T13:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你諗下你點思考咪知鬼點思考囉</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大腦未死味思考到囉 唔通死左佢個腦仲活動？"},{"pid":"fdafaa4153a5ea831ec696a2e125964cf9b5e148","tid":303672,"uid":27821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁現實係冇鬼，有咩可以討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪問緊信既人"},{"pid":"a33df53a38e9b3a0163a5fe8bbb6845b442a4caa","tid":303672,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T13:16:38.000Z","msg":"其實鬼點會有杉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3c36aa9e5bfbe03021eda24838120c055025db","tid":303672,"uid":90329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實鬼點會有杉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我聽見過果啲人講話無衫 得個頭同個身白色一舊"},{"pid":"9eed93ede6d2c3e35e670bfea1e06b7539ce2939","tid":303672,"uid":27821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T18:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0b41b9d29ef20bc4a7f0c20500e94adbed7b39","tid":303672,"uid":27821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9eed93ede6d2c3e35e670bfea1e